item.description:
Join us for dinner and Irish music!

We will be going to the Winsor House in Duxbury on Wednesday November 15 at 6:30PM. Music starts at 7PM and is played until 9PM. We will be in the pub area of the restaurant which includes traditional pub fare including burgers, flatbread pizza, fish and chips, raw bar, and buffalo chicken. If you would like to see the menu beforehand please visit http://winsorhouseinn... and scroll down to the pub menu.

We will enjoy good food and music in a relaxed, fun atmosphere. Don?t miss an opportunity to meet and get to know each other, as well as talk about different foods, restaurants, and meals we enjoy. This will also be a great time to plan our next Dining Out event.

Restaurant: Winsor House, 390 Washington St, Duxbury, MA ~ 781-934-0991

Directions: please visit http://winsorhouseinn..., you can also get door to door directions at the bottom of the page

Cost: meal, shared apps, drinks, plus tax, tip and beverages

Please see our "About Us" page for full details.

Please bring cash. You are responsible for your portion of the meal, including but not limited to, your drinks, food, tax, and tip and any shared items.

Organizer: Jen

When and Where:
Wednesday November 15 at 6:30PM
Winsor House, Duxbury, Ma

Suggested Event Fee:
USD1.00 per person donation

RSVP Deadline: All Maybe's must be changed to Yes or No by 10am the day of the event (Nov 15th). (Please Note the Organizers reserve the right to presume you will not be attending if you do not update your Maybe RSVP accordingly.) Please finalize your RSVP by 10am on Wednesday, November 15th.
